Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.67,0:00:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,从前 发生了一场叫「废弃战争」的大战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.14,0:00:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在这场漫长的战争中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.26,0:00:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,出现了一群人称「击坠王」的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他们带着白色闪耀的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.32,0:00:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,将打倒敌人的个数刻在身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.45,0:00:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,发挥出了超乎人类智慧的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.84,0:00:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,随着和平的到来 击坠王们便不见了踪影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,传说中的击坠王?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.49,0:02:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是真人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,慌什么 一群蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他在虚张声势
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,仔细想想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,击坠王是三百年前的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,人类怎么可能活得这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:02:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.55,0:03:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 曹长说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.55,0:03:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,看我们怎么收拾你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,小阳菜 把眼睛闭上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,听我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,人呢? 你干了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么搞的?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.43,0:03:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,人呢? 那家伙人在哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,人呢? 卑鄙小人给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,曹长…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.03,0:04:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,在走路而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 还回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,从她身上夺走的点数
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,她怀着对妈妈的信任走过的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,5年时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:04:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是传说中的击坠王 在发脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,竟敢这么对我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.56,0:05:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,光杀了你还不够解气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,看我把你剁成肉酱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么? 我可是天选之人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能有人躲得开我的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能 我的剑是全伊里尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,最快的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,被看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,挥舞着等身长的大太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,左手刻着-999点数的 传说中的击坠王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他的脚力超乎人类智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,依靠肉眼看不见的动作消灭敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,因此得名 「闪击的击坠王」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么这么快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,可他的点数不是-999吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,既然是负的 不是很弱吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是他被女生甩掉的次数
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 你睁眼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:06:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我在天上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.71,0:07:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 害怕吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.51,0:07:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,难以置信 人竟然能在天上飞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,也许吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.77,0:07:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,果然里希特先生 就是我一直在找的击坠王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧收拾掉 把你的点数夺回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你还饿着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,饿着?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,回去以后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我请你吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 我一定会夺回你的点数
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:07:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是说点数
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你别受伤 求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,受伤的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,别乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定会请你吃饭的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,小阳菜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我要夺回你的点数
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,回去之后 和你一起吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,说定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.02,0:09:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,要我停手吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,别…别打了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 小阳菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样? 我没受伤哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.53,0:10:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 手臂还灵活着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,阳菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.91,0:10:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你去找
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,传说中的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,击坠王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是 是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我终于找到了 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.91,0:11:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,0:11:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这个我就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,捞到个好东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,数字球能卖好大一笔钱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这下从明天起我也变有钱人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特先生真是的 你这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你这女人真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,还不懂吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.70,0:11:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我的点数是5700
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你是760
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不乐意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.16,0:11:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要赌星吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一直在找你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么? 不想白给吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这个就给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.27,0:12:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,迷你呕吐酱玩偶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.94,0:12:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈她…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我去找击坠王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,除了我还有别人也被叫做「击坠王」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈妈说的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.16,0:12:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,小阳菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事啊 小阳菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.89,0:13:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈的遗物也被拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,现在一头雾水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我到底
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.92,0:14:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,以后该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,小阳菜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,总之 这个玩偶先拿着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,玩偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦 拿着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你很快就会懂了 该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是你的数字球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:15:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,数字球这个东西 只要持有就是重罪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,在阿尔西亚 是最重的罪行之一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.69,0:15:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,真像那傻子会干的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你老老实实把数字球交给军队
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,就不会被问罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但你拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,而且还被军队的人看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这样下去 你一辈子都会被军队追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:15:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不只是军队
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,想要数字球的地痞流氓数不胜数
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不被人夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你这不谙世事的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕连三天的安全都无法保障
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.32,0:16:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.20,0:16:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,一直
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,都在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,自从妈妈不在以后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我无依无靠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,多少年 多少年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:17:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,都一个人在路上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,其实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.73,0:17:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我好孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,一个个城镇找过去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,到头来 也只是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得自己以后都会孤苦伶仃的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我好孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这座镇上遇见了里希特先生和奈奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常 非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.22,0:17:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,还是第一次 笑得那么开心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.73,0:17:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.03,0:18:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,回去之后我们一起吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不是说好的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.91,0:18:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特先生 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你这骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.96,0:18:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,到头来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:18:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,数字球在你手上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.14,0:19:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.10,0:19:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 你别误会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来就对数字球不感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我反倒 是来向你道谢的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,道谢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.49,0:19:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们才找到了击坠王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这下我终于能交出份不错的报告了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,给真正的长官
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.76,0:19:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,给真正的长官?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 话说真是厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,光走路就能把人震飞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,移动速度超过了音速吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.73,0:20:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,而最厉害的 就是那个高空下来的剑击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.94,0:20:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不 应该说是「爆击」吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那个重力加速度根本接不住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.53,0:20:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就算躲开一点 也会被下落的冲击波震飞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,该怎么破…哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.97,0:20:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,正如您所言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,到底…在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 错不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我亲眼看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.52,0:20:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,代号001 闪击的击坠王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.03,0:20:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特·巴赫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.95,0:20:54.95,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,730)}「我恨你」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.63,0:22:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊 我是里希特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.67,0:22:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,下集「星掠者」又是走光狂欢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.80,0:22:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,可这没办法啊 说到制服就不得不提内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,说到内裤就不得不提制服
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.18,0:22:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,别说假预告
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.97,0:22:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,下集「这是制服 没办法」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.88,0:22:40.40,Next,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1103,840)}下集「这是制服 没办法」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.60,0:22:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,————————OP————————
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.70,0:01:20.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}拖着沉重的脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.50,0:01:23.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}行走着寻找希望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.45,0:01:28.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}即使受挫 也迈出第一步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.30,0:01:32.40,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}无法分担的伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:35.10,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}被撕扯的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.10,0:01:40.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}如果需要同伴 我就在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.75,0:01:46.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}每个人都有自己不同的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.65,0:01:54.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}只要和大家一起 感觉任何愿望都能成真
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:57.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}{\pos(960,1035)}Forever Plunderer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:02:00.80,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}跟着走 即使迷失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:06.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}也想守护 吹散痛苦的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:12.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}让跨越未来的坚强 不输给迎面的风暴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:23.40,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}汇聚到一起吧 往日各自走过的遥远路途
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.70,0:01:20.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}重たい足引きずり
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.50,0:01:23.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}歩いて探す希望
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.45,0:01:28.75,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}めげそうでも 最初の一歩 踏み出そう
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.30,0:01:32.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}別けてくれない痛み
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.40,0:01:35.10,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}千切れそうになる心
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.10,0:01:40.75,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}誰かを求めるなら ここに私いるから
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.75,0:01:46.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}一人一人違った 星があるから
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.65,0:01:54.05,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}皆と一緒なら どんな夢も叶う気がする
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.00,0:02:00.80,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}付いていく 見失っても
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.80,0:02:06.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}苦しみ吹き荒れる 魂 守りたい
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.50,0:02:12.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}未来を超える強さが 嵐に負けぬように
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.90,0:02:23.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}重ねようよ 別々に 数えた実った遥かな道
